{
  "Id": 880000010,
  "Name": "燃烧的光玉",
  "Description": "马琪正在尝试联络你，而这似乎与先行公约最近筹划的名为《第二索拉》的大型项目有关……",
  "MaleTexture": "",
  "FemaleTexture": "",
  "AreaIcon": "",
  "QuestId": 880000010,
  "ShowQuestList": [],
  "QuestDesc": "马琪正在尝试联络你，而这似乎与先行公约最近筹划的名为《第二索拉》的大型项目有关……",
  "Conditions": [],
  "Chapters": [
    {
      "Dialogues": [
        {
          "Id": 1,
          "Speaker": "马琪",
          "PlotLineKey": "今天要制作的游戏场景是这样的……",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": []
        },
        {
          "Id": 2,
          "Speaker": "马琪",
          "PlotLineKey": "在这一卷的末尾，主角终于要和无冠者展开决战。",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": []
        },
        {
          "Id": 3,
          "Speaker": "马琪",
          "PlotLineKey": "原著里写道“……黑暗如山般压向了我们……我们的剑与矛早已断裂，法杖上的宝石也已破碎……”",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": []
        },
        {
          "Id": 4,
          "Speaker": "马琪",
          "PlotLineKey": "“而无冠者的身影几乎遮蔽了夜空……它睥睨着我们，目光如刀……”",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": []
        },
        {
          "Id": 5,
          "Speaker": "马琪",
          "PlotLineKey": "“……纵使只有手中<color=highlight>燃烧的光玉</span>，我们亦要迈向那巨壁一般的敌人……”",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": []
        },
        {
          "Id": 6,
          "Speaker": "马琪",
          "PlotLineKey": "“……若荒野无处可归，那便行军踏向这世界的尽头。若长夜无光，那便举刀挥向那无能的月轮。”",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": [
            {
              "TextId": 261,
              "PlotLineKey": "听得我热血沸腾。",
              "PlayVoice": false,
              "JumpToId": null
            },
            {
              "TextId": 262,
              "PlotLineKey": "很期待这个场景制作出来。",
              "PlayVoice": false,
              "JumpToId": null
            },
            {
              "TextId": 263,
              "PlotLineKey": "这里该播一段气势磅礴的音乐。",
              "PlayVoice": false,
              "JumpToId": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "Id": 7,
          "Speaker": "马琪",
          "PlotLineKey": "作为第一卷的高潮，第一次看到这里时我和你一样激动。我也很期待在游戏中还原这个场景。",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": []
        },
        {
          "Id": 8,
          "Speaker": "马琪",
          "PlotLineKey": "但是只有一点，大家都想象不出<color=highlight>燃烧的光玉</span>的样子……",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": []
        },
        {
          "Id": 9,
          "Speaker": "马琪",
          "PlotLineKey": "虽然在之前的章节也有提到过它，但作者并没有详细地描写它的外观。",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": []
        },
        {
          "Id": 10,
          "Speaker": "马琪",
          "PlotLineKey": "要是能找到它的参考的话，大家应该就能还原出决战的场景了。",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": []
        },
        {
          "Id": 11,
          "Speaker": "马琪",
          "PlotLineKey": "如果你有找到合适的东西的话，可以随时过来交给我。",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "Dialogues": [
        {
          "Id": 1,
          "Speaker": "马琪",
          "PlotLineKey": "原来如此……这个东西的确很符合我对燃烧的光玉的想象。",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": []
        },
        {
          "Id": 2,
          "Speaker": "马琪",
          "PlotLineKey": "我现在就把这个交给开发人员。相信有了它，大家就能够制作出最后的场景了。",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": []
        },
        {
          "Id": 1,
          "Speaker": "Speaker_undefined",
          "PlotLineKey": "",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": []
        },
        {
          "Id": 1,
          "Speaker": "马琪",
          "PlotLineKey": "到这里，小说里天城篇的场景就全部制作完成了。",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": []
        },
        {
          "Id": 2,
          "Speaker": "马琪",
          "PlotLineKey": "非常感谢你给予先行公约的帮助，{PlayerName}。",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": [
            {
              "TextId": 392,
              "PlotLineKey": "场景非常好看。",
              "PlayVoice": false,
              "JumpToId": 3
            },
            {
              "TextId": 393,
              "PlotLineKey": "期待能尽早玩到游戏。",
              "PlayVoice": false,
              "JumpToId": 4
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "Id": 3,
          "Speaker": "马琪",
          "PlotLineKey": "我也觉得很好看。",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": [],
          "JumpToId": 5
        },
        {
          "Id": 4,
          "Speaker": "马琪",
          "PlotLineKey": "我也很期待。等有了进一步的消息，我会马上告诉你的。",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": [],
          "JumpToId": 5
        },
        {
          "Id": 5,
          "Speaker": "马琪",
          "PlotLineKey": "顺带一提，卡尔先生也知道了你的名字，说如果有机会一定要见你一面。",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": [
            {
              "TextId": 394,
              "PlotLineKey": "能和作者见面是我的荣幸。",
              "PlayVoice": false,
              "JumpToId": 6
            },
            {
              "TextId": 395,
              "PlotLineKey": "他是不是要给我什么特别礼物？",
              "PlayVoice": false,
              "JumpToId": 7
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "Id": 6,
          "Speaker": "马琪",
          "PlotLineKey": "卡尔先生也表示很感谢你帮助他的小说改编游戏的开发。",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": [],
          "JumpToId": 8
        },
        {
          "Id": 7,
          "Speaker": "马琪",
          "PlotLineKey": "这我就不清楚了，等你以后见到卡尔先生了亲自问他吧。",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": [],
          "JumpToId": 8
        },
        {
          "Id": 8,
          "Speaker": "马琪",
          "PlotLineKey": "总之，目前事情就告一段落了。但是……",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": [
            {
              "TextId": 396,
              "PlotLineKey": "但是什么？",
              "PlayVoice": false,
              "JumpToId": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "Id": 9,
          "Speaker": "马琪",
          "PlotLineKey": "开发组的成员都很喜欢你提供的物品参考。在游戏之后的章节如果还有需要，还可以再拜托你吗？",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": [
            {
              "TextId": 397,
              "PlotLineKey": "当然可以。",
              "PlayVoice": false,
              "JumpToId": null
            },
            {
              "TextId": 398,
              "PlotLineKey": "价钱到位，都好说。",
              "PlayVoice": false,
              "JumpToId": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "Id": 10,
          "Speaker": "马琪",
          "PlotLineKey": "那就太好了，你可以放心，先约一定不会在报酬上吝啬的。",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": []
        },
        {
          "Id": 11,
          "Speaker": "马琪",
          "PlotLineKey": "那么，下次见啦，{PlayerName}，期待和你之后的合作。",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "Dialogues": [
        {
          "Id": 1,
          "Speaker": "马琪",
          "PlotLineKey": "其实……关于今天的参考物品，有位书迷有一些自己的看法。",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": [
            {
              "TextId": 345,
              "PlotLineKey": "是哪位？",
              "PlayVoice": false,
              "JumpToId": null
            },
            {
              "TextId": 346,
              "PlotLineKey": "在哪个位置？",
              "PlayVoice": false,
              "JumpToId": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "Id": 2,
          "Speaker": "马琪",
          "PlotLineKey": "他的名字叫斜阳，白天应该在今州书院附近就可以找到他。",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": []
        },
        {
          "Id": 3,
          "Speaker": "马琪",
          "PlotLineKey": "他对小说的诸多场景都很有自己的看法，也给我们提了很多意见，可是……",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": [
            {
              "TextId": 347,
              "PlotLineKey": "可是什么？",
              "PlayVoice": false,
              "JumpToId": 4
            },
            {
              "TextId": 348,
              "PlotLineKey": "他很难相处吗。",
              "PlayVoice": false,
              "JumpToId": 5
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "Id": 4,
          "Speaker": "马琪",
          "PlotLineKey": "可是……他说的话很难懂。",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": [],
          "JumpToId": 6
        },
        {
          "Id": 5,
          "Speaker": "马琪",
          "PlotLineKey": "不，那倒不是。他只是说的话很难懂……",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": [],
          "JumpToId": 6
        },
        {
          "Id": 6,
          "Speaker": "马琪",
          "PlotLineKey": "大家虽然能够感受到他对《第二索拉》的热情，但都觉得和他沟通起来很困难。",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": []
        },
        {
          "Id": 7,
          "Speaker": "马琪",
          "PlotLineKey": "但是我感觉，如果是你的话，也许可以听懂他在说什么。",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": [
            {
              "TextId": 349,
              "PlotLineKey": "我去找找他看看。",
              "PlayVoice": false,
              "JumpToId": 9
            },
            {
              "TextId": 350,
              "PlotLineKey": "我的确很懂中二病和谜语人。",
              "PlayVoice": false,
              "JumpToId": 8
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "Id": 8,
          "Speaker": "马琪",
          "PlotLineKey": "虽然我不懂你说的词是什么意思，但听起来你很有信心的样子。",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": [],
          "JumpToId": 9
        },
        {
          "Id": 9,
          "Speaker": "马琪",
          "PlotLineKey": "那么就拜托你啦。",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "Dialogues": [
        {
          "Id": 1,
          "Speaker": "斜阳",
          "PlotLineKey": "那无能的月轮，是主角对无冠者不仁的控诉……",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": []
        },
        {
          "Id": 2,
          "Speaker": "斜阳",
          "PlotLineKey": "而燃烧的光玉，是寂夜里绽放的光明的新芽……",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": [
            {
              "TextId": 294,
              "PlotLineKey": "好！大文豪！",
              "PlayVoice": false,
              "JumpToId": null
            },
            {
              "TextId": 295,
              "PlotLineKey": "好难懂……",
              "PlayVoice": false,
              "JumpToId": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "Id": 3,
          "Speaker": "斜阳",
          "PlotLineKey": "终于有人主动来问我《第二索拉》的事了……天地可鉴，我一定是这本书最忠诚的粉丝。",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": []
        },
        {
          "Id": 4,
          "Speaker": "斜阳",
          "PlotLineKey": "只有这本书中的广阔世界，能承载我如不歇之泉般时刻满溢的文采！",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": [
            {
              "TextId": 296,
              "PlotLineKey": "那你觉得燃烧的光玉是什么？",
              "PlayVoice": false,
              "JumpToId": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "Id": 5,
          "Speaker": "斜阳",
          "PlotLineKey": "从听说你帮助先约开始制作游戏起，我就料到，你一定会来问我这个问题。",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": [
            {
              "TextId": 297,
              "PlotLineKey": "为什么你这么肯定？",
              "PlayVoice": false,
              "JumpToId": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "Id": 6,
          "Speaker": "斜阳",
          "PlotLineKey": "为什么？因为这燃烧的光玉，是那场震天撼地的决战里逆转局势的关键！",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": []
        },
        {
          "Id": 7,
          "Speaker": "斜阳",
          "PlotLineKey": "如此不可一世的宝贝，你在俗世里自然是寻不到参考物的。",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": [
            {
              "TextId": 298,
              "PlotLineKey": "那要在哪里才能找到？",
              "PlayVoice": false,
              "JumpToId": null
            },
            {
              "TextId": 299,
              "PlotLineKey": "还请大师给我一个明示。",
              "PlayVoice": false,
              "JumpToId": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "Id": 8,
          "Speaker": "斜阳",
          "PlotLineKey": "既然你如此诚心地发问了，我就告诉你……这种东西，只有在那变幻莫测的<ano=声之领域>索诺拉</ano>中才能找到。",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": [
            {
              "TextId": 300,
              "PlotLineKey": "声之领域……",
              "PlayVoice": false,
              "JumpToId": null
            },
            {
              "TextId": 301,
              "PlotLineKey": "大师高明！",
              "PlayVoice": false,
              "JumpToId": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "Id": 9,
          "Speaker": "斜阳",
          "PlotLineKey": "但这可为难不了作为忠实粉丝的我，我早已备好了东西。",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": []
        },
        {
          "Id": 10,
          "Speaker": "斜阳",
          "PlotLineKey": "现在，我就可以把这个珍贵无比的参考物送给你。",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": []
        },
        {
          "Id": 11,
          "Speaker": "斜阳",
          "PlotLineKey": "但是，我有个条件。",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": [
            {
              "TextId": 302,
              "PlotLineKey": "什么条件？",
              "PlayVoice": false,
              "JumpToId": null
            },
            {
              "TextId": 303,
              "PlotLineKey": "大师请讲。",
              "PlayVoice": false,
              "JumpToId": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "Id": 12,
          "Speaker": "斜阳",
          "PlotLineKey": "那就是……你问问马琪，能否把我斜阳的大名也附属在游戏的感谢名单上。",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": []
        },
        {
          "Id": 13,
          "Speaker": "斜阳",
          "PlotLineKey": "我头号粉丝的名头，必须要人尽皆知才行。",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": [
            {
              "TextId": 304,
              "PlotLineKey": "我可以帮你问问。",
              "PlayVoice": false,
              "JumpToId": null
            },
            {
              "TextId": 305,
              "PlotLineKey": "这个事情先行公约说了才算数。",
              "PlayVoice": false,
              "JumpToId": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "Id": 14,
          "Speaker": "斜阳",
          "PlotLineKey": "反正……辛苦你帮我问问。我斜阳，尽人事，听天命！",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": [
            {
              "TextId": 306,
              "PlotLineKey": "好的大师。",
              "PlayVoice": false,
              "JumpToId": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "Id": 15,
          "Speaker": "斜阳",
          "PlotLineKey": "东西在这，你拿去吧。答应我的事可别忘了！",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": []
        }
      ]
    },
